channel.title: Project No-Name
channel.description:
This was recently a project I was coding for my friend a while back.
[b]Things to do - [/b] Correct Vesta's Armour. Finish making a custom KBD place. Finish my custom Mini-Game. Add Chaotic weapons. Add D2H GFX.
Few more things, which I will list later.
[b]Things done -[/b]
Quest Tab edited. Dragon Claws added. Spirit Shields added. Vesta's Spear added. FunPK. Fixed Vengeance. Added "Veteran" and "Donator." Added EP drops. Custom chest, which gives you random PvP items per 5 swamp tars. Added SoL. Fixed Donator shop. Added 100% KBD breathe. Vesta's LongSword 100% (Degrades) Statuis Hammer, 100%.
Theres more, I'll list later.
[b] [center]This is what the server is looking like so far.
Dragon Claws [IMG]http://img812.imageshack.us/img812/323/dragonv.jpg[/img]
Customs [IMG]http://img52.imageshack.us/img52/9032/inventa.jpg[/img]
PkP [IMG]http://img26.imageshack.us/img26/5125/pkps.jpg[/img]
PkP Shop [IMG]http://img684.imageshack.us/img684/1017/shopmh.jpg[/img][/center]
[center]Stat Spec [IMG]http://img535.imageshack.us/img535/9807/20288394.png[/img][/center]
More coming soon. :)
